<a class="anchor release_tag" name="v0_13_0"></a>
<h1><a href="#v0_13_0">Tag: v0.13.0</a></h1>

##### Branch: 'master'

##### by Stephen McGinty on 08-Jun-2017 03:24AM


* Added a [global session](http://origen-sdk.org/origen/guides/misc/session/#Global_Sessions)
  to allow data to be easily exchanged between all of a
  user's Origen application workspaces (Corey Engelken)
* Added Regex#to\_txt method (Brian Caquelin)

~~~ruby
regex = /abc/i
regex.to\_txt                    # => "\/abc\/i"
regex.to\_txt(no\_mods: true)     # => "\/abc\/"
~~~

* Removed dependency on GCC (Brian Caquelin)

