object.

<a class="anchor release_tag" name="v0_12_0"></a>
<h1><a href="#v0_12_0">Tag: v0.12.0</a></h1>

##### Branch: 'master'

##### by Stephen McGinty on 24-May-2017 21:06PM


* Added support for driving custom waveform codes on V93K (will also work on any other tester that
  supports such a thing), see: 
  [http://origen-sdk.org/origen/guides/pattern/v93k/#Driving_Custom_Waveforms](http://origen-sdk.org/origen/guides/pattern/v93k/#Driving_Custom_Waveforms)
* Added APIs to define and consume timing waveforms, see:
  [http://origen-sdk.org/origen/guides/pattern/timing/#Complex_Timing](http://origen-sdk.org/origen/guides/pattern/timing/#Complex_Timing)

